{"tid":2087102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7.1見】我用左首動漫歌總結左直到上年六月尾的反修例運動","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:02:15.000Z","uid":6477,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1bda09b904797d08913bc16ab13d37a0ed426598","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"可能開錯台既關係，個POST 係創意台出左成半個鍾都零回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以係時事台開多次！<br />\n希望打破零回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vzxan1RQLGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvzxan1RQLGU&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=8ae51102\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vzxan1RQLGU</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW 講樣緊要野先，<br />\n可以既話都想大家今晚出POST既主題前面都好似我咁，加<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【7.1見】</span></strong>，<br />\n希望可以令到成個熱門都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【7.1見】</strong></span>做開頭，<br />\n凝聚民氣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回到正題，<br />\n反送中運動過左一年多少少，<br />\n有好多事我地都已經冇得返轉頭，<br />\n但我地可以回望過去，吸收過往經驗以作改進。<br />\n就好似今時今日既香港民主進程都有過好多唔同既碰撞<br />\n由雨傘既失敗、分化，再到反送中既和勇不分就係一個好好既例子。<br />\n所以，我就特登整左呢條片俾大家回望過去，<br />\n睇番我地一開始係點樣由港豬走上街頭，<br />\n由假期去深圳玩到而家假期上街表態，支持黃店。<br />\n就算今晚就立國安法，但我相信香港人都唔會咁易就退讓。<br />\n就好似今次我所用既《飆速宅男》其中一首主題曲 リマインド咁，<br />\n(リマインド解作提醒)<br />\n我地要不斷提醒自己，<br />\n唔可以忘記<br />\n黑警既暴行、手足既犧牲、政權既不公義！<br />\n但願香港人可以堅定，撐過呢段黑暗既日子。<br />\n香港人，7.1見<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果識我真人既就唔好相認，THANKS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf92d3426ba52a3c3a0b6e2e52682b54af9784ef","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"66e8140498c813deb619dda9666e5f571a5e0cfa","tid":2087102,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297398306ca315988a67a4a59fb784508f04d6bd","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1979126a82a1c1184cec2cb0761ecb649397832","tid":2087102,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTcqtv8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTcqtv8.jpg&h=e8794907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFUsGQ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFUsGQ8.png&h=fe7230d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d40b5a1be940d05e36e01c9bf32a1d1c8df1cea3","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6062359e2e0662d7b515926e34a5ec37673fedb2","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93c24dcb1a86860ba4048ccbfdbd4802f90a1953","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4a153a71d64bbfd8de1e8450a0af280ffe87211","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0f216422da240f2236fee2f334be4277e2871b3","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2639c0dae076851d8aaefc2499703b2e5d3fa717","tid":2087102,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5547d493df40cdabc4443c496214e3f775d72c8","tid":2087102,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERfrQoJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k